{"tid":2429810,"cid":16,"subCid":0,"title":"【韓式炸雞】原味同辣醬做法 附食譜","createTime":"2021-03-02T14:13:24.000Z","updateTime":"2021-03-07T20:18:30.000Z","uid":393786,"like":17,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"1e161ed57bc2c01c42f96963476b23080bbd5201","tid":2429810,"uid":393786,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-02T14:13:24.000Z","msg":"試過用現成炸粉,感覺一般般,自已調個槳仲脆同埋好味<br />\n大家不仿可以睇下影片,如果拍攝有咩不足希望可以俾下意見小弟<br />\n新頻道需要大家支持<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />我希望每星期起碼做一道菜式同大家分享<br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/0xkaI53RDxM\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2F0xkaI53RDxM&d=a689Ea%2B9Xr9H89nGruQQA7PGlnsopddeS9pLw%2Bq5tFI%3D&h=06d7631b\" target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/0xkaI53RDxM</a><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/scoAayH.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FscoAayH.jpg&h=a5d46218&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n跟我呢個配方包保無失敗<br />\n韓式炸雞   <br />\n配料Ingredients :<br />\n雞翼/雞腿肉 ------------------------------- 400g<br />\n洋蔥粉 -------------------------------------- 1茶匙<br />\n蒜粉 -------------------------------------- 1茶匙<br />\n甜椒粉 -------------------------------------  1茶匙<br />\n白胡椒粉----------------------------------- 1/2茶匙<br />\n料酒 -------------------------------------- 1湯匙<br />\n鹽 ------------------------------------- 1茶匙<br />\n<br />\n炸粉/炸槳:<br />\n多用途麵粉(中根麵粉)----------------- 250g<br />\n鷹粟粉/栗米粉--------------------------- 60g<br />\n發粉  ------------------------------------1湯匙<br />\n洋蔥粉 ------------------------------- 1湯匙<br />\n鹽 ------------------------------------- 1茶匙<br />\n雞蛋 ------------------------------------- 1隻<br />\n黑胡椒粉----------------------------------- 1/2茶匙"},{"pid":"4705657c000cb95592e0a6bf6fc81bc912584707","tid":2429810,"uid":79793,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-03-02T14:15:05.000Z","msg":"十點出post 拉<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail2